data.description: Welcome to this spacious 2-bedroom, 2-bath home adorned with modern finishes. Recently painted both inside  and out, it boasts a lovely backyard with scenic canal views. Inside, you'll find new doors, updated bathrooms, and  sleek stained concrete flooring throughout. The kitchen is equipped with stainless steel appliances for your  convenience. Not to mention, a generously sized enclosed Florida room offers a cozy space to relax. Additionally,  the barrel tile roof is just 8 years young. This residence is nestled in a welcoming 55+ community, providing a  perfect place to call home.
